documentation:
Argparse parses checksums as {'checksum_sha256': '<sha256_hash>'}

Return a list of these arguments in a format the Identifiers Service
understands:

"checksums": [
  {
    "function": "md5",
    "value": "fobarbas"
  },
  {
    "function": "sha256",
    "value": "foobarbaz"
  }
],

Note: This modifies the values in 'arguments'
